# Portfolio Backend v1.0

Backend powering my AI-powered developer portfolio.

## Features

- AI Chatbot (RAG)
- Markdown Knowledge Base
- Groq LLM Integration
- GitHub Analytics Sync
- LeetCode GraphQL Sync
- Background Scheduler
- REST APIs
- Intelligent Caching

## Tech Stack

- Node.js
- Express
- Groq
- GraphQL
- Axios
- node-cron

## Installation

npm install

cp .env.example .env

npm run dev